Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.70,0:00:03.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,SERN will take the time machine.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.24,0:00:06.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,SERN? What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.75,0:00:09.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Makise Kurisu.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.29,0:00:10.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okabe Rintarou.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.83,0:00:12.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hashida Itaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.59,0:00:14.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You three are coming with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.92,0:00:19.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about Mayuri?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.22,0:00:22.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shiina Mayuri is...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.68,0:00:25.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...not needed.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.31,0:00:30.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.56,0:00:34.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.02,0:00:39.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For FB... FB... FB...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.64,0:01:03.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayuri?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.18,0:01:05.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayuri!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.31,0:01:10.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayuri?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.15,0:01:19.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.62,0:01:27.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get away from her.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.04,0:01:33.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okabe, get away from her!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.54,0:01:35.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She'll kill you, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.42,0:01:40.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll pay for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.63,0:01:42.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make her pay for this!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.20,0:02:13.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,42.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.79,0:02:16.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,CRT.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.63,0:02:19.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's on.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.09,0:02:25.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.31,0:02:36.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okabe!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.52,0:02:37.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.31,0:02:39.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if it fails...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.94,0:02:41.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do it now!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.11,0:02:46.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okabe!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.78,0:02:52.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leap!
