Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.05,0:04:35.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Mayuri was still in elementary school
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.89,0:04:39.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}when her grandmother died.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.35,0:04:43.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She went to the grave every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.02,0:04:47.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even six months after her grandmother's death,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.78,0:04:49.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}she was still going.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.16,0:04:53.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She always had her grandmother's pocket watch in her hand,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.33,0:04:57.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and she was always, always looking up at the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.29,0:05:03.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Like she was waiting for her grandmother to come and get her.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.63,0:05:08.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And then one day, there was a ray of light.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.76,0:05:17.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It was the kind called Rembrandt Lighting,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.43,0:05:21.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}or an angel's ladder.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.39,0:05:25.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It felt like the light was drawing her up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.65,0:05:32.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Like she was going to disappear...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.07,0:05:32.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayuri!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.74,0:05:39.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okarin...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.79,0:05:41.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let it take you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.16,0:05:44.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're my hostage.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.25,0:05:45.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to be my hostage.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.79,0:05:47.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll use you for human experiments.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.71,0:05:50.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The words that came out of my mouth
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.05,0:05:52.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}were from some show I'd seen as a little kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.93,0:05:56.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Mayuri and I had watched it together.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.80,0:06:00.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Some mad scientist, screaming like an idiot...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.85,0:06:03.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.98,0:06:10.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So Mayushii is your hostage, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.74,0:06:15.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, I guess I can't go, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.21,0:06:34.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.84,0:06:36.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Were you napping?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.44,0:06:49.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What time is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.61,0:06:51.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What time is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.57,0:06:53.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.11,0:06:54.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's almost five.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.07,0:06:56.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're going shopping, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.95,0:06:58.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shopping...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.16,0:07:01.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll order pizza.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.62,0:07:02.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.62,0:07:04.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just don't get the tropical special.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.66,0:07:05.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hate that thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.83,0:07:07.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Agreed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.62,0:07:11.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The time leap worked?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.30,0:07:12.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okabe?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.38,0:07:14.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Mayuri? Where is she?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.97,0:07:17.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with you, all of a sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.22,0:07:22.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayushii said she was going to Miss Ruka's, \Nto invite her to the party, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.77,0:07:25.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going shopping?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.81,0:07:27.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The development conference is canceled.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.81,0:07:28.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Canceled?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.90,0:07:29.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.52,0:07:31.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.02,0:07:33.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're done here for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.69,0:07:35.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Both of you, go home now!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.65,0:07:36.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.61,0:07:37.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just go home!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.82,0:07:39.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay? Do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.95,0:07:42.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.70,0:07:45.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His phone starts ringing, and then...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.00,0:07:48.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Phone?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.96,0:07:54.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Mayushii.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.67,0:07:56.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't answer the phone right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.51,0:07:59.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you'd like to leave a message...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.55,0:08:05.81,Default - margin,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There's nothing to indicate that the world line changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.81,0:08:08.14,Default - margin,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's different than the D-mail.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.14,0:08:10.77,Default - margin,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I really am back at 5:00 PM.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.86,0:08:15.82,Default - margin,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the bullet train!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.82,0:08:19.82,Default - margin,,0000,0000,0000,,No, the bullet train is white.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.57,0:08:24.37,Default - margin,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}After this, Mayuri will return with Suzuha.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.87,0:08:28.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Should I go to the police?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.71,0:08:31.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No, who'd believe me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.33,0:08:32.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That I've come from the future?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.25,0:08:35.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Three hours left...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.46,0:08:37.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I have to do something!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.59,0:08:39.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayuri!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.97,0:08:40.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayuri?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.68,0:08:44.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Oka... No, Kyouma{\fscx80}-
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.18,0:08:45.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Mayuri?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.18,0:08:47.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sh-She already left.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.72,0:08:48.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Left?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.56,0:08:49.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.39,0:08:52.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Thirty minutes ago, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.31,0:08:54.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She said she was going back to the lab.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.65,0:08:56.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't she get back?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.48,0:08:58.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.65,0:09:03.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was so nice of you to invite me to the party, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.20,0:09:05.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did she say she was stopping anywhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.28,0:09:07.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayuri-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.37,0:09:08.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.12,0:09:11.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you see her, tell her to call me right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.67,0:09:13.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.38,0:09:16.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If the world line hasn't changed,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.34,0:09:19.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}then if I don't do anything different,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.63,0:09:22.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}she should do the same things as last time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.84,0:09:23.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Where is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.01,0:09:26.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nyan-nyan!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.18,0:09:28.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Feyris can't answer the phone right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.72,0:09:30.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you need something...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.73,0:09:38.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you, Mayuri?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.11,0:09:41.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayuri?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.15,0:09:42.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.11,0:09:44.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Assistant...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.87,0:09:46.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you, we're done today.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.70,0:09:47.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go home{\fscx80}-
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.53,0:09:48.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be honest.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.54,0:09:51.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You time leaped from the future, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.63,0:09:57.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How could you tell?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.38,0:10:01.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The second you answered the phone, you seemed to change.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.47,0:10:03.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From the way you're acting,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.05,0:10:04.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can guess that something happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.76,0:10:05.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.22,0:10:08.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I don't have time to give you the details.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.22,0:10:10.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just run.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.56,0:10:12.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run? Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.43,0:10:13.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.98,0:10:15.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just get away from the lab.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.73,0:10:16.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.36,0:10:19.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me later, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.48,0:10:22.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Tell Daru, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.03,0:10:23.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.57,0:10:24.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okabe...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.70,0:10:25.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.32,0:10:28.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't do anything weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.24,0:10:31.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.96,0:10:36.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okabe Rintarou!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.58,0:10:38.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, where's Ochanomizu{\fscx80}-
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.38,0:10:40.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you seen Mayuri?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.05,0:10:42.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shiina Mayuri?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.38,0:10:45.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She just invited me to your party{\fscx80}-
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.34,0:10:45.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.97,0:10:47.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Turn right, up there...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.05,0:10:51.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, which way is Ochanomizu?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.27,0:10:54.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to take Nae shopping...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.35,0:10:55.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ask at the police box!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.77,0:10:58.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And once you've taken her, don't come back!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.61,0:11:00.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.23,0:11:01.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll tell you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.54,0:11:18.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayuri...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.17,0:11:20.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayuri!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.84,0:11:22.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okarin!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.05,0:11:23.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look! It's the first star!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.76,0:11:25.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.72,0:11:27.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just come with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.84,0:11:29.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about the party?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.68,0:11:32.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's canceled. I told Kurisu and Daru.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.68,0:11:34.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.31,0:11:36.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll tell you later!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.06,0:11:38.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I asked Suzu-san to come, too,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.27,0:11:39.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and Daru-kun was ordering pizza...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.86,0:11:41.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just listen to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.90,0:11:44.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okarin...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.03,0:11:46.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.45,0:11:53.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayushii doesn't understand...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.45,0:11:57.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You always do things I don't understand,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.08,0:12:00.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but today, I really don't understand you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.21,0:12:04.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you really want to do the experiment, after all?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.92,0:12:06.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayuri...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.55,0:12:12.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.47,0:12:15.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But just for now, can you listen to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.02,0:12:18.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.27,0:12:21.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll explain the details later, I promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.77,0:12:23.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.82,0:12:27.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry. Mayushii just got scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.69,0:12:29.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.03,0:12:31.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not your fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.58,0:12:41.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are so many people here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.54,0:12:43.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's rush hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.59,0:12:46.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.00,0:12:48.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But no one's at the platform...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.05,0:12:52.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once again,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.26,0:12:55.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the following lines have been shut down, due to a bomb threat.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.68,0:12:58.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They said they don't know when the trains will start again.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.64,0:13:00.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How stupid of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.81,0:13:01.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not now...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.90,0:13:02.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okarin?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.90,0:13:05.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayuri, get to the subway now!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.94,0:13:07.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okabe Rintarou, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.86,0:13:13.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.16,0:13:18.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're coming with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.29,0:13:20.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you standing there for?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.91,0:13:22.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Move!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.87,0:13:23.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.13,0:13:31.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.22,0:13:33.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run, as fast as you can!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.85,0:13:37.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.22,0:13:40.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okarin!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.10,0:13:40.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go, quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.39,0:13:42.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run, Mayuri!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.87,0:14:06.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shiina Mayuri was the one who died.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.21,0:14:07.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okabe-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.29,0:14:10.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, Okabe Rintarou has been captured.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.71,0:14:11.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayuri!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.80,0:14:15.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.55,0:14:16.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let you kill her!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.80,0:14:20.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,2000)}Mayuri, I will save you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.56,0:14:23.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll save you...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.69,0:14:29.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...no matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.03,0:14:37.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Canceled?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.99,0:14:38.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.87,0:14:40.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.45,0:14:43.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.25,0:14:45.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got word
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.75,0:14:48.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that Mr. Braun is planning to return tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.34,0:14:51.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okarin, did you do something again?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.34,0:14:53.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I suppose so.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.55,0:14:54.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But what about Mayuri?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.72,0:14:56.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll talk to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.26,0:14:59.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's dangerous to be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.10,0:15:00.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're done here for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.43,0:15:05.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Was I too forceful?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.98,0:15:07.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.10,0:15:09.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It doesn't matter if I was acting weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.86,0:15:13.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}For now, I just need them away from the lab!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.86,0:15:17.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Mayushii.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.53,0:15:19.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't answer the phone right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.87,0:15:25.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Why is it taking so long?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.33,0:15:28.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's going to end up like last time!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.08,0:15:29.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I need to find Mayuri.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.70,0:15:33.20,Celly,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be2\pos(891,605)\frz20.296}Rukako
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.80,0:15:37.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.38,0:15:39.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rukako! It's me! Okabe!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.51,0:15:41.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oka... I'm sorry, Kyouma{\fscx80}-
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.89,0:15:43.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Mayuri?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.01,0:15:44.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is Mayuri there?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.31,0:15:46.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayuri-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.10,0:15:46.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.81,0:15:47.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's just heading bac{\fscx80}-
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.81,0:15:49.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop her!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.06,0:15:52.65,Default - margin,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell her not to move until I get there!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.65,0:15:54.28,Default - margin,,0000,0000,0000,,She said she was going back to the lab.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.28,0:15:56.32,Default - margin,,0000,0000,0000,,Just do as I say!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.32,0:15:57.82,Default - margin,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.82,0:15:59.36,Default - margin,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayuri-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.29,0:16:05.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the bullet train!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.33,0:16:08.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, the bullet train is white.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.58,0:16:11.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayuri!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.42,0:16:13.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okarin!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.09,0:16:19.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.59,0:16:21.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was about to go fix Fubuki-chan's costume,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.80,0:16:23.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and then go to the lab.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.85,0:16:25.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fubuki-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.02,0:16:26.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A cosplay friend of yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.10,0:16:27.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.31,0:16:31.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She said a thread on the costume I made came undone.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.15,0:16:32.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just got a message from her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.19,0:16:34.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So that's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.07,0:16:36.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once it's fixed, I'll go right to the lab,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.82,0:16:38.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so I'll make it to the party.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.53,0:16:40.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait. The party...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.53,0:16:41.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The party was cancel...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.28,0:16:44.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, it was postponed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.12,0:16:46.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.41,0:16:48.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't use the lab.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.46,0:16:50.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It can't be helped. {DOKI HAVE INVADED CR}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.54,0:16:53.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.17,0:16:56.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I wanted you to come with me for a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.05,0:16:58.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.42,0:16:59.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about Fubuki-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.42,0:17:01.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, but do it later.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.26,0:17:02.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's an emergency.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.47,0:17:05.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, did something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.06,0:17:08.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, we're going to be away for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.56,0:17:09.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On a trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.94,0:17:12.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Together?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.60,0:17:13.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.36,0:17:18.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can put Fubuki-chan off till tomorrow,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.19,0:17:19.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but this is very sudden.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.40,0:17:20.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are we going?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.74,0:17:22.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll tell you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.49,0:17:24.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't have much time to catch the train.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.37,0:17:28.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Mayushii isn't ready at all, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.20,0:17:30.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.12,0:17:31.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.29,0:17:34.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Okarin!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.00,0:17:36.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.75,0:17:37.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.80,0:17:39.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,G-Goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.84,0:17:41.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, bye-bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.31,0:17:52.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't Akihabara Station that way?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.02,0:17:53.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're taking the subway.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.98,0:17:55.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.70,0:18:12.58,Default - margin,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a really long time
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.58,0:18:14.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,since you pulled me along like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.50,0:18:16.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.76,0:18:30.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're heading back.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.06,0:18:31.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.91,0:18:52.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.41,0:18:53.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
