Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.67,0:19:00.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kurisu, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.73,0:19:17.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My watch isn't working...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.85,0:19:19.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.27,0:19:21.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just wound it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.82,0:19:28.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are so many people here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.62,0:19:30.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Sobu line shut down.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.33,0:19:32.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut down?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.99,0:19:34.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.79,0:19:37.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A bomb threat was called in.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.29,0:19:40.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.84,0:19:45.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Okarin.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.93,0:19:48.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.30,0:19:52.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayushii has a lot of places she wants to go,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.06,0:19:54.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but it's okay for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.06,0:19:57.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In exchange,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.60,0:20:00.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,when this is over, I want you to tell me everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.07,0:20:05.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.45,0:20:08.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.49,0:20:12.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.66,0:20:18.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry I can't help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.05,0:20:27.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's have that party sometime.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.76,0:20:30.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.97,0:20:32.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sometime.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.10,0:20:39.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sometime...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.27,0:20:41.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.40,0:20:48.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayuri-oneechan!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.24,0:21:36.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.08,0:21:39.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't mean to...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.21,0:21:47.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just wanted to surprise her...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.10,0:21:59.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let you kill her!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.89,0:22:02.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.44,0:22:05.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...save Mayuri!

